	<Title>
		Shingles treatment: Does alcohol use affect therapy?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Generally, it&apos;s best to avoid alcohol during the course of shingles treatment.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Does moderate alcohol use interfere with shingles treatment?
	</Question>
